&lt;p>If you need review from the corporate communications team on a potential incident, gather information in an issue or link us to the Slack discussion by message the team in the #corpcomms Slack channel and we’ll work with the Security Communication Manager on Call to determine next steps&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="incident-communication-plan">Incident Communication Plan&lt;/h2>
